high_descs: Head forward to the white column then turn left and walk to the right black stand; the stand that is holding the golden trophies
Pick up the trophy that is on the right
Turn to your right and cross the room, then turn left and face the tall floor lamp
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a trophy under a tall lamp

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the rightmost black cabinet with the trophies on it.
Pick up the right trophy.
Turn right and walk to the lamp.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: View a trophy by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Walk to the white column, then turn left and walk to the black cabinet.
Pick up the right statue on the black cabinet.
Turn around, then turn left and walk towards the window, turn left, look up, and turn on the white lamp.
Examine the statue under the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine the statue under the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the trophies.
Pick up the trophy on the right.
Walk over to the lamp still holding the trophy and look up at the lamp.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp while holding a trophy.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the dresser
Pick up the statue on the right side of the dresser
Turn to the right and go to the window then turn to the left and hold the statue up to the lamp shade
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue by the light of the tall lamp

high_descs: Go left to face the black cabinet with two statues on it.
Pick up the statue on the right.
Move the the right to face the lamp in the corner.
Turn the lamp on.
anns.task_desc: Turn a lamp on while holding a statue under it.
